      "widgets_values": [
        "RPG Monster Generator + ControlNet Depth Workflow\n\n[Setup]\n1. Place a dungeon reference image at: ComfyUI/input/dungeon_ref_01.png\n2. Download ControlNet model: xinsir/controlnet-depth-sdxl-1.0\n   -> place at: ComfyUI/models/controlnet/controlnet-depth-sdxl-1.0.safetensors\n3. Install ComfyUI-ControlNet-Aux via ComfyUI Manager (for MiDaS preprocessor)\n\n[Tuning]\n- ControlNet strength (node 6): 0.6-0.85 (start at 0.8)\n- ControlNet end_percent (node 6): 0.7-0.85 (let creature dominate later)\n- Lightning offsets in RPG node: -22 steps, -6.0 cfg (preset for Oil Painting)\n\n[Replacing reference]\nDuplicate node 2 (LoadImage) per scene type, or swap files in ComfyUI/input/."
      ],
